      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen in pristine condition. This vehicle has been curated to an uncompromising standard, exhibiting a level of preservation typically reserved for showroom displays. Every aspect of this motorcar\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its meticulously maintained mechanical systems\u2014reflects a legacy of superior care. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of peerless quality.",
