      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You are absolutely going to love this ride. I have babied this car from day one, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like a total dream and is just waiting for someone who will appreciate how special it is. Come grab this beauty before someone else does!",
      "price": 43500.0,
