    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a peerless 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, presented in collector-grade condition. This example is powered by the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system that has been fully serviced with Beisan components. To ensure long-term mechanical reliability, the rod bearings have been proactively replaced and the rear subframe reinforced with precision-welded plates. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp gate entry, transferring power through a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its original torsional rigidity, with no bushing deflection or oil seepage from the constant-velocity joints. Every aspect of the drivetrain and suspension geometry remains in factory-optimal alignment, offering the linear power delivery and tactile steering feedback synonymous with the chassis's peak performance. This is a turn-key, investment-quality icon.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No scratches or mechanical issues. Full service records included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
